text.paragraph:
Inform patients that anaphylaxis has been reported with ingredients contained in tramadol hydrochloride. Advise patients how to recognize such a reaction and when to seek medical attention 


  [see Contraindications (4); 


   Warnings and Precautions (5.16); 


   Adverse Reactions (6)]


  .
